<p>Due to a miscommunication between the contest organizers and the deletion teams, Doomsday Contest articles that fell below the deletion threshold were deleted early.<br />
In light of this, it was decided to temporarily resurrect any deleted pages on the Sandbox, and provide links to said sandbox pages on the Doomsday Contest page under the corresponding team's hub. This way, the articles could still be viewed without the problem of vote resetting.</p>
<p>If you have any Doomsday Contest articles that were deleted, please put the text of the article into a Pastebin and PM them to either myself, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/zyn" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1404533); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1404533&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1529031131" alt="Zyn" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1404533)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/zyn" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1404533); return false;">Zyn</a></span>, or <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/jacob-conwell" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1372582); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1372582&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1529031131" alt="Jacob Conwell" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1372582)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/jacob-conwell" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1372582); return false;">Jacob Conwell</a></span>, so that we can put them into a sandbox and link them from the contest page.</p>

